data.description: Welcome home to Kirkwood subdivision! Located in the desirable Double Churches and Northside High school districts, this beautiful 3 BR 2 BA home is waiting for you. Roof, water heater & refrigerator only 1 year old! The home is convenient to shopping, dining, and activities. Open floorplan with dining area and great room with gas fireplace, plus a large bonus room. Most of the home has beautiful wood floors, the kitchen has porcelain tile, and the bathroom floors are LVP. The bonus room has carpet.  Guest bath has updated walk-in shower with built in bench. The private backyard has new privacy fence, landscaping, and a large covered 2 car carport and patio. It is like your own personal park, and perfect for relaxing and having your morning coffee. There is also an outlet to hook up an RV in the back if desired. Motivated Seller, so make your appointment today! Seller can do lender required repairs only if that can be paid from closing.
